fields.name: Sprayfill 2K Polyester Sprayable Bodyfiller 3.7L
fields.description: Excellent adhesion on various substrates including GRP, Metal, Wood, Polyester Laminates, and Hard Plastic. Features excellent flow and filling properties, suitable for large areas and deeper imperfections. Drying time 20-30 minutes, sanding grade P120-320.

fields.name: Multifunctional Lightweight Putty 4.5Kg
fields.description: 25% lighter than standard putties, offering very easy application and sanding without paper clogging. Ideal for larger surface areas.

fields.name: Glass Fibre Reinforced Putty 1.8Kg
fields.description: Designed for all deep filling and bridging works. Comes with excellent sanding properties and can be used on a wide range of applications.

fields.name: 2K Easy Sand Flowable Filler 1L
fields.description: A flowable polyester filler putty for finishing, blending, and skim coating bodywork. Adheres well to steel, aluminium, and fiberglass. Less porous with higher resin content for reduced moisture penetration.

fields.name: Diamond Clear 2K HS Clear Anti Scratch 1L
fields.description: High gloss with excellent UV stability and resistance. Provides an efficient drying time to match all conditions, offering great appearance and durability.

fields.name: Full Body Clear Coat Fast Air Dry 1L
fields.description: Extremely fast drying with a good finish and high gloss. Suitable for air drying and polishing post-application.
